
1/ Install docker ce

	https://docs.docker.com/install/linux/docker-ce/ubuntu/

2/ Build docker image

	sudo ducoker build -t dapp-java:latest -f Dockerfile.java .
	sudo ducoker build -t dapp-exec:latest -f Dockerfile.java .

3/ Run cc container

	sudo docker run -it --memory=10m --cpus="0.01" -v $PDX_HOME/dapps:/dapps/ dapp-java HelloWorld.jar
	sudo docker run -it --memory=10m --cpus="0.01" -v $PDX_HOME/dapps:/dapps/ dapp-exec test 

	Here, the memory and cpus limits are from chaincode deployment requirements, which tie to the cost
        of deploying a chaincode.
 
